{"tid":1198942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔知我聽日去做到啲咩","createTime":"2019-06-10T11:06:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T18:42:52.000Z","uid":143708,"like":172,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"8a7457cda81a1b8bae42d21423053a9d8757b99e","tid":1198942,"uid":143708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:06:27.000Z","msg":"我只係一個普通，體能弱，無做開運動，打兩下都無力嘅女仔，<br />\n我知，如果比警察捉到，我無可能反抗到，<br />\n甚至乎還手對於佢地嚟講就好似r痕咁。<br />\n<br />\n我唔敢衝。<br />\n我唔敢衝唔係怕痛，怕死，怕比人拉，<br />\n係怕我根本就無力打鬥，到時如果比犬捉咗，又會辛苦巴打想救我返嚟，然後更多巴打陷入危險，我怕我越幫越忙。<br />\n又或者一去到，咩都未做就已經比犬捉咗，白白地將自己送比犬立功or交差。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但我都會照去。</span><br />\n我會做我能力範圍內做到嘅嘢，例如送物資，企後啲幫手，咩都好。<br />\n再喺無得選擇嘅情況下，我先同大家一齊衝。<br />\n去咗，當係後備都好。<br />\n<br />\n呢啲叫做衡量過自己能力，唔係<span style=\"color: red;\">無用</span>。<br />\n我身邊已經有人上連登見到啲人話無用無用，<br />\n而決定聽日後日唔出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「你無留低一齊衝，對得住香港？」<br />\n「出嚟行完就返屋企有咩用？」<br />\n「唔衝，你出嚟把鬼咩。」</span><br />\n<br />\n喂，係邊個前一兩個星期不斷叫人去遊行，話咩多一個都好多，幾點去都唔遲？<br />\n完咗就話啲人淨係嚟行，咩用都無，根本就係知道後尾林奠仲係要推送中，先嚟馬後砲鬧只參與咗遊行嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n明明之前就係你地宣傳叫人去遊行，無叫過人去衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。以我所知，最後衝出去嘅原因係因為11點嗰份新聞稿同警犬開始做嘢，<br />\n唔包括在一直以嚟對於6月9號嘅宣傳入面。(有錯請更正)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(咁但係應該好多人都同我一樣，去之前都諗過，遊行咋喎，威脅唔到政府啲咩，佢會咁順攤咩？<br />\n但行行下又覺得有成百萬人又創咗回歸後新高，我係on9有抱過希望真係靠遊行可以推倒修例，都係完咗先知自己嗰陣發緊夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。)</span><br />\n<br />\n但係只去遊行，無衝唔代表無用！<br />\n我唔係和理非，但至少琴日我地香港人有噠着返好似雨革嗰陣團火，我地團結返，知道仲有咁多同路人，<br />\n而且件事已經傳到去好多國家關注，你諗下如果琴日嘅遊行只有幾萬人嘅話，你叫其他國家點去幫你，你自己人都唔爭氣要外人幫你爭氣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你係咁勁一早就知琴日遊行完林鄭會照推送中，<br />\n咁你一早就唔好搞遊行，你應該搞示威，或者你眼中有用嘅嘢，唔好調返轉話無留低無衝嘅人，在場根本無人指揮無人知道要點做。<br />\n超過百萬嘅人數去遊行，係有佢一定嘅作用，<br />\n啲人係咁話無用，講埋啲晦氣說話，只係打擊緊士氣，sorry我眼中呢樣先係真正嘅無用。<br />\n你想人同你一齊衝，唔應該話乜嘢係無用，<br />\n應該講清楚 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你覺得乜嘢係有用</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府可以無視百萬人遊行，仍然強制性推送中條例，<br />\n我地就更加要企硬，企出嚟。<br />\n唔好令到身邊嘅人覺得做乜都無用，灰哂心唔想出嚟。<br />\n我見到琴日好多人好勇敢同班警犬打過，甚至有無咁打得嘅女仔，老人家，又有年輕過我嘅人，又有好多人都睇唔起嘅00後，<br />\n仲有比人拉咗嘅義士。<br />\n多謝你地嘅付出，對唔住我當時幫唔到啲咩。<br />\n香港市民唔應該令你地嘅付出白費，<br />\n聽日，後日，大家一齊企出嚟，<br />\n因為有爭取過，先有資格話呢個政府有幾仆街。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GKNRLWZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGKNRLWZ.png&h=f9c0eb6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41b94dcc73a788ff96bcc0fe9eec2a4c6b575055","tid":1198942,"uid":157550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:07:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb809c19a3a9774ce6b4a14c280f3bf9ccc439ef","tid":1198942,"uid":162866,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:07:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住帶電筒</span></span>"},{"pid":"e1120ae8d1a5fff129e27525573e511d1962e509","tid":1198942,"uid":217807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:08:50.000Z","msg":"唔緊要 我都會去"},{"pid":"6229c368211b73a6eadf4b2f1fd68110770e9ffa","tid":1198942,"uid":5523,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:12:15.000Z","msg":"我夜晚睇完電視<br />\n我覺得我係懦夫<br />\n我連生存都唔知做到D咩<br />\n何故當天不不羈的心今天竟變了柒頭?"},{"pid":"ac9e425c38f01fa0eaa9e9d98bd0a3e39c674e57","tid":1198942,"uid":247639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:12:16.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"0112173c5b60e88c793b3adbae5b57c7b73da8a8","tid":1198942,"uid":143708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41b94dcc73a788ff96bcc0fe9eec2a4c6b575055","tid":1198942,"uid":157550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:07:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:13:36.000Z","msg":"到時見，唔撚好灰心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0433b72e7bb3d717a66d8afb4993ee0fcc8c1876","tid":1198942,"uid":143708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:33:03.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推，希望更多人睇到，唔好怪隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a1f100a292b65cd4fcdeb4210ad99f5223e37b4","tid":1198942,"uid":84511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:34:36.000Z","msg":"帶電筒 帶水"},{"pid":"1c8ebc4abe76bacd93a2322da0551458b5083d5e","tid":1198942,"uid":143708,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5a1f100a292b65cd4fcdeb4210ad99f5223e37b4","tid":1198942,"uid":84511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:34:36.000Z","msg":"帶電筒 帶水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:36:40.000Z","msg":"收到，聽日我同成班朋友一齊帶物資過去！"},{"pid":"e9ca448d3cbd9fa28954b956b468d48975963028","tid":1198942,"uid":184389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:38:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"122322234895b4e96a881c58ad3e886649bbca4c","tid":1198942,"uid":143708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:51:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"495025c0fd37e0fcc7d35464c534c5dbadda846c","tid":1198942,"uid":143708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:08:08.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"634e874d338219c4cfc305c6598617675918638c","tid":1198942,"uid":157550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:10:21.000Z","msg":"如果個個都好似你咁樣諗就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ab07ee5244adcf8685568af0cc0fdba73d71ac","tid":1198942,"uid":206812,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:11:07.000Z","msg":"香港而家先回歸咗22年 距離50年不變都未行夠一半<br />\n已經各方面被控制 剝削自由<br />\n我哋嘅下一代 條路只會越來越難行<br />\n趁我哋仲有力 仲有機會企出嚟 唔好放棄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後 有無巴絲願意好似上次咁 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一齊印單張喺各區派傳單</span></span><br />\n宣揚罷工罷市 呼籲大家再出嚟<br />\n時間已經係唔足夠 但如果人數都唔夠嘅話 <br />\n我哋咩籌碼都無曬<br />\n上次都係要靠大家鍥而不捨宣傳 先叫到百幾萬人出嚟<br />\n上年紀嘅人 佢哋無連登 無ig 消息無我哋咁靈通<br />\n求下各位巴絲 一齊幫下手"},{"pid":"574e6768b7293dcd30ee555942c7011eb417bf3b","tid":1198942,"uid":71253,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:12:54.000Z","msg":"連啊婆都唔驚比狗圍，我地驚咩<br />\n<br />\n絲打萬事小心"},{"pid":"c770716f7d219626c4a6095a04f17bc5cb540c63","tid":1198942,"uid":222960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5ab07ee5244adcf8685568af0cc0fdba73d71ac","tid":1198942,"uid":206812,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:11:07.000Z","msg":"香港而家先回歸咗22年 距離50年不變都未行夠一半<br />\n已經各方面被控制 剝削自由<br />\n我哋嘅下一代 條路只會越來越難行<br />\n趁我哋仲有力 仲有機會企出嚟 唔好放棄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後 有無巴絲願意好似上次咁 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一齊印單張喺各區派傳單</span></span><br />\n宣揚罷工罷市 呼籲大家再出嚟<br />\n時間已經係唔足夠 但如果人數都唔夠嘅話 <br />\n我哋咩籌碼都無曬<br />\n上次都係要靠大家鍥而不捨宣傳 先叫到百幾萬人出嚟<br />\n上年紀嘅人 佢哋無連登 無ig 消息無我哋咁靈通<br />\n求下各位巴絲 一齊幫下手"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:14:03.000